Thumbs.db

# Claude Code local tool state (not project source)
.claude/

# macOS/cloud-sync duplicate artifacts ("foo 2.ts"). Enumerated by extension (NOT a broad
# "* 2.*") so a legitimately-named "step 2.md" is never silently swallowed.
* 2.ts
* 2.tsx
* 2.js
* 2.mjs
* 2.cjs
* 2.json
* 2.md
* 2.sql
